      <data key="d2">0.95</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "when you log in and assuming you've got got matters they will be listed here the your view is split into four different views", "ts": 37.4, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "Welcome, Chantel Van Wyk (Main SA); Viewed | Favourites | Invitations | Renewals; Browse All Matters", "ts": 3.0, "source": "vision"}, {"quote": "the details that we've obviously inserted is it will display yes some of it at least so the patient details the names the date of birth their deceased status then of course the instructions that were that were selected uh the services", "ts": 1533.4, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "rowan reid | MedBrief. Client: Building Solicitors &amp; Consulting. Billing code. Matter number: ee 8000NID-mwm. Tabs: Matter dashboard / Records / Radiology / MedBrief Match / Users / Disclosures / Communications / Download.", "ts": 1568.688, "source": "vision"}]</data>
