    <node id="claim:0004">
      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Standard matter licence is two years, then annual renewal; clients can delete before renewal</data>
      <data key="d2">0.95</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "for most clients when they open a matter there's a two-year period where they pay a a license fee for two years and then after those two years it renews for one year so most some of them have have like a one-year period before it renews some of them have maybe a three-year period but the the norm is usually a two-year period", "ts": 80.2, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "they do still have the opportunity to to delete it if they don't want it to renew um if they delete it obviously it doesn't renew if they don't delete it then it does renew", "ts": 112.3, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:01"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The standard matter licence period is two years, then renews annually. Some clients have one-year or three-year initial periods. If a client does not delete the matter before the renewal date, it renews automatically.</data>
      <data key="d21">person:chantel-van-wyk</data>
      <data key="d22">[]</data>
      <data key="d23">fact</data>
      <data key="d24">False</data>
      <data key="d25">80.2</data>
    </node>
