      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Super-admins see three matter-creation options; regular clients see only classic or wizard</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "because i'm logged in as a made brief super admin i i can see all three options like adding a new client which clients obviously can't see they will usually have the option to see either creating a new matter classic or just creating the current new matter", "ts": 131.7, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:02"]</data>
      <data key="d20">A MedBrief super-admin sees three matter-creation options: add a new client, create a matter (classic), and create a matter (wizard). Regular clients see only the classic or wizard options.</data>
      <data key="d21">person:chantel-van-wyk</data>
      <data key="d22">[]</data>
      <data key="d23">fact</data>
      <data key="d24">False</data>
      <data key="d25">131.7</data>
    </node>
