      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "supporting documents is just for um obviously consent forms that the user has given consent for their medical records to be requested from whichever medical institution that's usually if the records are if request records request is selected as a service we have to have that consent form", "ts": 252.5, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "if the person is deceased then we will need a a certificate of of death that type of thing", "ts": 268.5, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:03"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The supporting documents page collects consent forms (form of authority) required for records requests and, if the patient is deceased, a death certificate.</data>
