      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "we mostly do clinical negligence cases but we are also venturing into personal injury it's not it's not that you know the the proportion of uh our cases or the matters on years it's still quite small in terms of personal injury but there is that option now", "ts": 461.8, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
