      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "there's a little bit of inconsistency um across the product sometimes the clients are referred to as clients and sometimes the client is referred to as an area storage area so it's just it's just inconsistency okay we do need to fix that but yes if you ever do see come across area it refers to the client", "ts": 526.7, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:04"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The terms "area" and "client" are used interchangeably but inconsistently across the MedBrief product. Wherever "area" appears, it refers to the client.</data>
