    <node id="claim:0016">
      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Review-before-sorting is a preference flag, not a chargeable service</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "do you want to review your clients records before they have sorted have been sorted now this isn't really a service it's just sometimes clients when we do get the the records they they want to review the records themselves before they continue with any services so it's just for us to be aware that before we do anything they do want to review it", "ts": 593.8, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:04"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The "review before sorting" wizard option is not a billable service but a preference flag that tells MedBrief the client wants to review their records before any further services proceed.</data>
      <data key="d21">person:chantel-van-wyk</data>
      <data key="d22">[]</data>
      <data key="d23">fact</data>
      <data key="d24">False</data>
      <data key="d25">593.8</data>
    </node>
