      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "early case assessment is exactly what it is it's performed on records that are not sorted so the clinicians go through it and just to see if there's a case or there is not a case", "ts": 624.5, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:04"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The early case assessment service is performed on unsorted records: clinicians review them to determine whether a case exists.</data>
