      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "schedule of radiology is pretty much like the chronology but it's it's just for radiology so it's just the list of all the different studies um that were submitted in in date order and the source where it was from", "ts": 696.0, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:04"]</data>
      <data key="d20">A schedule of radiology is similar to a chronology but covers only radiology: a date-ordered list of all studies submitted, with their source.</data>
