      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "the team i'm also not going to add this is sometimes i'm actually not quite sure when they use it but sometimes it might be a different team so like a specific team that works on clinical negligence for example or personal injury even though the matter can't specify it um but they that's it's it's a client internal use field", "ts": 838.7, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:05"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The team field is described as a client-internal use field, possibly used to indicate which internal team handles the matter (e.g. clinical negligence team vs personal injury), but Chantel is not certain of its exact use.</data>
      <data key="d21">person:chantel-van-wyk</data>
