      <data key="d25">838.7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="claim:0023">
      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Additional contacts receive the same automated and digest emails as the matter manager</data>
      <data key="d2">0.95</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "with all the automated emails that we send out to the clients for example if we've received records requests or the progress on on a clinical one of the clinical reports or perhaps one of the digest emails", "ts": 877.9, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "the additional contacts those emails will go to the matter manager as well as the additional contacts so that's all that is because sometimes the matter manager is not the only person well it might not be there or they might have a a um like a secretary or pa um that that does all the administrative stuff", "ts": 903.6, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:05"]</data>
      <data key="d20">Automated emails (records request receipts, clinical report progress, daily digest) go to both the matter manager and any additional contacts added to the matter, to accommodate PAs or secretaries.</data>
      <data key="d21">person:chantel-van-wyk</data>
      <data key="d22">["artifact:digest-email"]</data>
      <data key="d23">fact</data>
      <data key="d24">False</data>
      <data key="d25">877.9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="claim:0024">
      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Limitation date is the deadline by which a patient must make a claim</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "the limitation that you know what the limitation date is no it's it's sort of like a warranty date so um the same way you've got a three-year warranty when you when you buy i don't know a dvd player or something it's it's like that so the client would have or the patient would have three years or five years or ten years or whatever that that limitation period is to to complain or to to put a claim in", "ts": 964.4, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:05"]</data>
      <data key="d20">The limitation date is the deadline by which the patient must bring a claim, analogous to a warranty period (three, five, or ten years depending on case type).</data>
      <data key="d21">person:chantel-van-wyk</data>
      <data key="d22">[]</data>
      <data key="d23">fact</data>
      <data key="d24">False</data>
      <data key="d25">964.4</data>
    </node>
