      <data key="d2">0.95</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "depending on the case type it would already have two patients so you'll get mother's details and child's details", "ts": 1075.7, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "i should have actually just backtracked a little bit so with the case type i hate the fact that you can't that it doesn't give me the list unless i i replace it um or delete it sorry so with obstetrics obstetrics uh case types", "ts": 1046.0, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:06"]</data>
      <data key="d20">When an obstetrics case type (e.g. brain injury, maternal injury) is selected, the wizard automatically creates two patient records: one for the mother and one for the child.</data>
