      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Creating a batch request pre-populates fields from the existing matter to save administrators time</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "so what this is done is create the batch some with some of the information already and that i've just shown you instead of them creating it from scratch having to select this the center name etc or the trust name um so that's what this helps but it helps with", "ts": 1909.4, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:12"]</data>
      <data key="d20">Linking and creating a batch request from the matter dashboard pre-populates fields such as the medical institution and trust name, saving administrators from entering data from scratch.</data>
