    <node id="claim:0046">
      <data key="d0">Claim</data>
      <data key="d1">Batches are only created when sorting is involved or radiology is received</data>
      <data key="d2">0.95</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "batches are not created for all records requests it we only create batches if there's a sorting session uh if there is if sorting was selected as a service", "ts": 1925.7, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "batches are also created if there's radiology so if there is a radiology that was received with the medical records then a batch will be created", "ts": 1951.2, "source": "transcript"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["chapter:12"]</data>
      <data key="d20">Batches are not created for every records request; they are created only when (a) sorting was selected as a service or (b) radiology records are received alongside the medical records.</data>
