      <data key="d25">2132.7</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "there's different stages within dark sorter so first it's the sorting and then it's the dating and then it's admissions and then there's the file note or the memo whenever they refer to memo it's also known as a file note but file note is actually the more the more commonly used one now um and then the qa so for each of these stages a clinician needs to be selected", "ts": 2132.7, "source": "transcript"}, {"quote": "Sorting sessions (0/1): Session ID 454 - MedBrief Session. Sorter: Chantel van Wyk (MAIN SA). Admission Sorter: Chantel van Wyk (MAIN SA).", "ts": 2313.5, "source": "vision"}]</data>
