      <data key="d37">A large flowchart/decision-tree diagram (opened from a local file) mapping the matter-creation process across lettered columns A to H. Column A holds the core stages (services, matter details, patient details); columns B to F branch through service steps such as records request, early case assessment, sort &amp; paginate, chronology and records collection, depending on the services chosen. Explains how the creation wizard's steps are conditionally driven by service selection.</data>
