      <data key="d37">The same matter-creation flowchart zoomed in on the left/start of the tree, highlighting the initial column A nodes (services -&gt; matter detail -&gt; patient detail) feeding into the branching service paths (records request, early case assessment, sort &amp; paginate, chronology, records collection, supporting documents, summary). Clarifies the entry sequence of the wizard.</data>
