      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "Confluence - Frequently Used Terms. Section: Service request management (on Matter Dashboard). opposing party. Annotated dashboard image: Records requests (1/4), Batches (1/5), Chronology requests (5/1), Additional requests (1/1), Sorting sessions (1/2). Definitions: Service Group - refers to the various service groups on the matter dashboard, e.g. Records requests, Batches, Chronology requests, Additional requests, Sorting sessions. Service Request - refers to each service required (i.e. widget created) within a service group. Service Option - there are different services available for each service group.", "ts": 1768.812, "source": "vision"}]</data>
